Quickstrike:



Quickstrike's eyes nearly flickered with excitement as he heard Megatron's 
work. Sub-Commander! His stuborness and agressive orders payed off. He 
finally got his way, and it was well worth it.

"Sure thing boss!" he said, trying to act modest. He made a quick salute, 
less than 2 seconds worth. He could barly keep his excitment down. He 
couldn't wait to see Shredder's face after he heard this.

"All we's gotta do is wait fer them two bots t' get back here wit' th' 
stasis pod." he said. He honestly forgotten their names.
